name: Wastelander Outpost #5
description:
Leaderboard: https://barrenoutposts.com

The Wastelanders favor blighted lands. They are masters of deceit, using shadows and lies to infiltrate other factions.

As a merchant, you have the power to lend aid to the Wastelanders. Every purchased edition saves 1 outpost. After 24 hours, all unsaved outposts will be burned.
